insert into "books" ("description", "image", "title") values ('Digital storage oscilloscopes have long since completely supplanted analog storage oscilloscopes and have reached a degree of sophistication and performance which enable them to rival the most advanced real time oscilloscopes. In this comprehensive handbook, which provides a practical vade mecum for the engineer, Ian Hickman describes how they work and how to use them to best advantage. A wide range of models is available. This book includes a guide to all makes and models and will be best kept beside the instrument for instant reference. It will also be a most helpful guide to the subject for students and trainees. Ian Hickman is an experienced designer and author of best-selling titles including ''Oscilloscopes: How to Use Them, How They Work'', Newnes Practical Radio Frequency Handbook'', ''Analog Electronics'' and ''Analog Circuits Cookbook''.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=a-840LcscLoC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Digital Storage Oscilloscopes');
