insert into "books" ("description", "image", "title") values ('This is the ninth in the 300 series of circuit design books, again contains a wide range of circuits, tips and design ideas. The book has been divided into sections, making it easy to find related subjects in a single category. The book not only details DIY electronic circuits for home construction but also inspiring ideas for projects you may want to design from the ground up. Because software in general and microcontroller programming techniques in particular have become key aspects of modern electronics, a number of items in this book deal with these subjects only. Like its predecessors in the 300 series, "308 Circuits" covers the following disciplines and interest fields of modern electronics: test and measurement, radio and television, power supplies and battery chargers, general interest, computers and microprocessors, circuit ideas and audio and hi-fi.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=rZDbnQ0siCYC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', '308 Circuits');
