insert into "books" ("description", "image", "title") values ('This is my first book to look at masculine personality specifically in terms of the 16 personality types of character and temperament identified by C. G. Jung and familiar to the millions who have taken the Myers-Briggs Type Inventory. The book presents men''s personality types as the Dreamers, the Thinkers, the Doers, and the Idea Men. It demonstrates how problems of communication arise as a result of differences in typology rather than by gender. It shows how a man''s relationships with colleagues, partners, parents, and children. It provides a wonderful framework to use for self-understanding and psychological healing.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=tcSeM_7ABmIC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Sixteen Men');
